    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 31 profile of Sam Brown, horse trainer and riding instructor, which failed to mention his employers, Montclair Riding Academy in New Jersey and Cedar Lane Stables in Brooklyn</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The My Job column on the Workplace page on May 31 about Sam Brown, a horse trainer and riding instructor, omitted the identity of his employers. They are the Montclair Riding Academy in New Jersey and Cedar Lane Stables in Brooklyn.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
